    "  <head>\n",
    "    <title>What I Did Over the Summer</title>\n",
    "  </head>\n",
    "  <body>\n",
    "    <h1>Going to the Beach</h1>\n",
    "    <p>At the beach, I did many things such as swimming, relaxing, and collecting seashells</p>\n",
    "  </body>\n",
    "</html>"
